{"tid":1449043,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:55.000Z","uid":147259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1133d07a49da7324a45a8c912f4f9621af926ba","tid":1449043,"uid":147259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:45:42.000Z","msg":"無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcphAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=5a5e753e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcphAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=81659873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"79dbd373f2cb3dad63e74964a2d162b6d8cac983","tid":1449043,"uid":57012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"推幫"},{"pid":"80e711bb2c89cb6c6cb39ac1defe5970b5715acd","tid":1449043,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536ffdfaad10c31e5ff1372af86646d0f4537303","tid":1449043,"uid":43211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:55.000Z","msg":"機場絕對唔可以成為戰場 唔係我驚傷到其他人 而係你地要跳海先有得走 我諗大家都明機場地勢如何 <br />\n<br />\n所以 我呼籲大家要制止任何過激行為 以防臥底點火"}]}